* BFP_CONV_2_INT             0x0200000000002000
* BFP_CONV_FROM_INT          0x0200000000004000
* BFP_FPSCR_ONLY             0x0200000000020000
* 
* Final : 0x0500000000000580, 0x0200000000006000, 0x0200000000020000

